<HEADLINE>
BRITAIN'S ECCENTRICS: THE STIFF UPPER LIP QUIVERS BEFORE AN
ECLIPSE 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
