<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-FARM-AID-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
IT'S RAINING FARM SUBSIDIES 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By TIM WEINER  
 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ City slickers may think there was some connection
