   BIKES-MOTORS _ DAYTON _ If you've been wanting to take advantage
of the Miami Valley's outstanding system of bike trails, but you're
not sure you're physically able to pedal long distances and up
hills, you might want to check out a bike with an electric motor to
supplement your muscle power. Bicycles are an energy-efficient way
of getting from place to place, and adding a motor can make a bike
easier to use. (Cummings, Dayton Daily News). 13. WITH PHOTO.
