justice, the next you're cheap-shotting someone with a folding
chair. So too with ``The Body'' who has been his usual bombastic
self at recent wrestling events. But at this week's National
Governors conference in St. Louis, he has been surprisingly quiet,
low-key and eager to learn, his colleagues say. Still, this is no
ordinary governor and heads still turn when Ventura enters the
room. Oscar Avila. 25
