   SCIENCE
</P>
<P>
   YUCCA_Mountain -- tk --(SCI-YUCCA-NUKE-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Cutaway view of the Nevada mountain.
</P>
<P>
   FINANCIAL
</P>
<P>
