<P>
   MIFFED-PUBLISHER (Montreal) _ Media mogul Conrad Black says the
prime minister is keeping him from being apointed to Britain's
House of Lords. That's why he's suing him. By Colin Nickerson. 800
words.
</P>
<P>
   FOREIGN-JOURNAL (London) _ It there's one thing that drives many
Brits crazy, it's the idea of Americans messing with their culture.
By Kevin Cullen. 700 words.
