got it right? By Jeff Jacoby.
</P>
<P>
   JORDAN-COLUMN (Undated) _ The $792 billion tax cut bill is so
bad for most Americans that no amount of criticism of the bill can
be overstated, or even exaggerated. By Robert A. Jordan.
</P>
