High School, according to testimony in a hearing Monday to decide
if he will be tried as an adult. TJ told friends that the problem
with the Columbine shooting was that the gunmen had specific
targets. He said if he was to shoot students at Heritage, he would
be more effective by shooting at random. (Stafford, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
