<P>
   WITH: CELL PHONE ETIQUETTE BOX _ Tips for using your cell phone.
(Lee, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes one 1-column B&AMP;W
photo of a cell phone.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: GEEK CHIC _ Pocket protectors aren't as common as they
