people during that tumultuous summer of moonwalks and Charles
Manson. And it stands as a milestone of Hendrix's career, certainly
one of his most famous concerts. It's part of a two-CD set released
recently. By DAVE FERMAN. Story has moved in ``e'' entertainment
category. &QL; 
