of a sitting First Lady Of The United States considering running
for an elective office is truly amazing. In New York City,
everybody has a ``Run, Hillary, Run'' bumper sticker on their car.
</P>
<P>
   Democrats put them on their rear bumpers.
</P>
<P>
   Republicans put them on the front.
