   (The story is scheduled to move by 8:30 p.m. ET.)
</P>
<P>
   CONDE-AD-COLUMN (Undated) _ Conde Net, the interactive division
of Advance Publications, is embarking on an elaborate advertising
and marketing effort to add more fizz to Phys.com, encourage
curiosity about Epicurious.com and stimulate computer users to
check in with Concierge.com. By Stuart Elliott.
</P>
<P>
   (The story is scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
</P>
