<HEADER>
A1130 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LADN-SPORTS-ADVISORY-     08-09 0032
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LADN-SPORTS-ADVISORY- </SLUG>
 
(For use by NYTimes News Service clients)  
