focus on cut, rather than decoration; satin shirt and shiny
trousers from Yves Saint Laurent's fall men's wear collection; a
ribbed see-through T-shirt draws on Saint Laurent's daring style of
the 1960s. (Dan Lecca/New York Times Photo) LITE
